      Prominent Rights Lawyer Gunned Down in Pakistan Court
      </mj-text>
      <mj-text color="#666869"  line-height="22px" font-size="18px"
      padding-top="0" padding-bottom="20px">
      Respected lawyer and human rights defender Abdul Latif Afridi was shot
       and killed inside the Peshawar High Court on Monday. Afridi was one of
        Pakistan's most courageous and outspoken voices for rule of law, 
        democracy, and human rights over several decades.
      </mj-text>

